result.name: Icelandic horse DNA sequence data
result.description: Two regions in the Icelandic horse genome, one in ECA4 and one in ECA9, were investigated with sequence data in relation to gaits. This investigation was a continuation of another paper published in December 2023; https://doi.org/10.1186/s12711-023-00863-6
result.center: The Swedish University of Agricultural Sciences, Dept. of Animal Biosciences and The Agricultural University of Iceland, Fac. of Agricultural Sciences
